# Cloudflare Pages — URL rewrites
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
#
# Status 200 = rewrite (the URL stays /lab/burn for the user, lab.html
# is served as the body). Status 301/302 would change the address bar.
#
# We rewrite to plain /lab.html (no query string) — Cloudflare Pages
# is finicky about query strings on the destination side of a rewrite
# and was silently dropping the request back to /lab in our first try.
# The lab.html JS reads location.pathname to figure out the mode, so
# the query string isn't needed.
#
# Single file behind three semantic URLs — no code duplication.

/lab/burn         /lab.html   200
/lab/crossbreed   /lab.html   200
